Package: gzip
Version: 1.2.4a
Revision: 3
Source: gnu
Essential: yes
Depends: base-files
PatchScript: mv -f INSTALL INSTALL.txt
CompileScript: ./configure %c
 make all
InstallScript: make install prefix=%i
 mkdir -p %i/share
 mv %i/man %i/share/
 mv %i/info %i/share/
 ln -s zcat %i/bin/gzcat
 ln -s zcat.1 %i/share/man/man1/gzcat.1
 ln -s zmore %i/bin/zless
 ln -s zmore.1 %i/share/man/man1/zless.1
CommentPort: Uses autoconf. Works fine, but needs some tweaking to put
 documentation in <prefix>/share.
Maintainer: Christoph Pfisterer <chrisp@users.sourceforge.net>
Homepage: http://www.gzip.org/
